      "content": "honestly sometimes i feel like i dont even exist. like i’m just drifting through this city and if i just stopped showing up tomorrow, it wouldn’t even change anything. no one here knows me and even the people back home feel like they’re talking to a version of me that died years ago. just an empty space.",
