    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm a burden to everyone. even when im talking to people, it feels like i'm just taking up space that could be used for something better. is it really so wrong to want to just stop... to just not have to deal with the noise and the heaviness anymore? it feels like a relief to think about it.",
